批量安装Nginx

---
- hosts: all
  tasks:
    - name: install nginx Written by pengchao Ma
      yum: name=nginx state=latest
    - name: start nginx
      service:
          name: nginx
          state: started
          enabled: yes


批量卸载Nginx

---
- hosts: all
  tasks:
    - name: Remove Nginx Written by pengchao Ma
      yum: name=nginx state=absent
    
          
